                {
                  "emoji": "📍",
                  "text": "<strong>Betweenness:</strong> Finding bottlenecks and bridge nodes."
                },
                {
                  "emoji": "🔗",
                  "text": "<strong>Closeness:</strong> Identifying the best-placed brokers."
