            "title": "Similarity: Who is Like You?",
            "box": {
              "list": [
                {
                  "emoji": "👯",
                  "text": "<strong>Jaccard Similarity:</strong> Intersection over union of neighbors."
                },
                {
                  "emoji": "📐",
                  "text": "<strong>Cosine Similarity:</strong> Comparing vector representations of nodes."
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "content",
            "title": "Pathfinding: How Do I Get There?",
            "box": {
              "list": [
                {
                  "emoji": "🗺️",
                  "text": "<strong>A*:</strong> Heuristic path search."
